        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And about the space of one hour after another confidently affirmed, saying, Of a truth this fellow also was with him: for he is a Galilean. And Peter said, Man, I know not what thou sayest. And immediately, while he yet spake, the cock crew.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " One spake in the name of the rest that were gathered about Peter, and he charges Peter confidently; and he might well, for John saith, ",
